The Yurt of Things (yot) - a simple event system for Arduino boards.
See http://www.ddimit.org for more information about the UfT lab.

arduino-sketches/
    Sketches (C/C++ code) for the Arudino toolchain. This includes the yot client and some test programs

arduino-libraries/
    Custom C/C++ libraries for the Arduino

easy_twitter/
    A Twitter library wrapper with OAuth information cached

pyramid/
    The Pyramid (formerly Pylons) WSGI server for making events public and general managment

scripts/
    Other Python scripts
